drugs.indications_raw_neofax:
Oral and rectal products are no longer manufactured in the US.
Sedative/hypnotic for short-term use only. Chloral hydrate has no analgesic properties;
excitement may occur in patients with pain.

drugs.administration_raw_neofax:
Give as an IV infusion by syringe pump over 30 minutes. Administer as a separate infusion
from penicillin-containing compounds. IM injection is associated with variable absorption,
especially in the very small infant.
